      "content": "hey so i have a question about my insulin. i usually take my basal dose in the evening but i barely ate anything for dinner tonight, like just a tiny bit of salad. would it be okay if i just skipped my dose tonight so my sugar doesnt crash too low? i'm kinda worried about going low if i dont eat much.",
