    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should follow the plan but i honestly feel like my dose is too high for when i don't eat much. it's better to be safe and not take it than to end up in the er from a low, right? if i just cut the dose in half tonight instead of skipping it entirely, would that be a safer way to go?",
